

###Block: Prestige Classes

# Cavalier
Weapon and Armor Proficiency		KEY: ~ Cavalier	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.CavalierClassAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:The cavalier is proficient with all simple and martial weapons, all types of armor, and shields.
Knowledge (Nobility and Royalty)	KEY: ~ Cavalier	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.CavalierClassAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:The cavalier gains +2 ranks in this skill automatically at first level.
Tall in the Saddle			KEY: ~ Cavalier	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.CavalierClassAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:The cavalier gains a bonus to his Ride skill check whenever he uses the Mounted Combat feat to negate a hit his mount takes in combat.
Deadly Charge				KEY: ~ Cavalier	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.CavalierClassAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:when mounted and using the charge action, you deal triple damage with a melee weapon (or quadruple damage with a lance), up to the number of times per day indicated. This ability supersedes the Spirited Charge feat.
Mounted Weapon Bonus			KEY: ~ Cavalier	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.CavalierClassAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:The cavalier gains a bonus to his attack roll when using the designated weapon while mounted.
Ride Bonus					KEY: ~ Cavalier	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.CavalierClassAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:The cavalier gains a competence bonus to Ride checks.
Burst of Speed (Ex)			KEY: ~ Cavalier	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.CavalierClassAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:At 3rd level, the cavalier ran urge his mount to greater than normal speeds, this ability doubles the distance of the mount's normal charge movement. This ability can be used once per day without penalty to the mount. Each additional use of the ability in a single day requires the mount to make a Will save (DC 20) immediately after the conclusion of the additional charge; failure results in the mount taking 2d6 points of damage.
Full Mounted Attack			KEY: ~ Cavalier	SOURCEPAGE:p.	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.CavalierClassAbility.SpecialQuality	DESC:At 6th level, the mounted cavalier may attack as a standard action when his mount moves more than 5 feet (assuming an opponent exists to be attacked), rather than as a partial action.



